 * always-load-me modules (for implementation firewalls of common arguments)
 * a facility like DBUS to communicate with other instances of rpcd (possibly serving the same app)
   * we need a facility like mutex to synchronize concurrent access eg. to Flatconfs /etc/fc
   * or take a multithreaded approach (embedded http server or mod_rpcd)

